## Next Recommendations
With the foundation built, here is what you should do next to gain maximum visibility:
1. **Google Business Profile Linking**: Go to your Google Business Profiles for The Rim, Stone Oak, and Bandera. Update the "Website" link on each profile to point to its *specific* new URL, not the main homepage.
2. **On-Page Content Polish**: Currently, the pages share the same base description from the template. You should edit each file to include unique local content (e.g., "Located right next to the Palladium in The Rim, Bakudan Ramen is the perfect pre-movie dinner spot.").
